    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-06-13T21:01:31Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDate>2016-04-20</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2016-04-20T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Philanthropic Enterprise Act of </strong> <b>2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt the holdings of a private foundation in any business enterprise that meet specified requirements relating to exclusive ownership, minimum distribution of&nbsp;net operating income for the charitable purpose (all profits to charity distribution requirement), and independent operation (not controlled by a substantial contributor or family members) from the excise taxes on excess business holdings. </p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
    </summaries>
